            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "While not entirely related to this issue (this one is error while **compiling** instead of runtime error), there is https://github.com/cython/cython/issues/2543 / https://github.com/cython/cython/issues/3929 which occasionally makes traceback not display the source code.\r\n\r\nFor what it's worth the linked issue above also causes IPython's traceback to not display the correct file, because of the algorithm `stack_data` uses. https://github.com/alexmojaki/stack_data/blob/master/stack_data/core.py#L622-L652  â†’ lead to a known bug in SageMath https://github.com/sagemath/sage/blob/develop/src/sage/repl/interpreter.py#L78",
